{"tid":2058946,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港逆潮流 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2020-06-10T14:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T14:04:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2abfec9a9d5d8a5db12995c2e4e00c8d7ad1e8","tid":2058946,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200610/20934127/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200610%2F20934127%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa08L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=b3552e7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200610%2F20934127%2F&h=ddae8b16\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200610/20934127/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港逆潮流 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200610/large/1591686102_c170.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200610%2Flarge%2F1591686102_c170.jpg&h=f96cd57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《新聞拍案驚奇》截圖<br />\n<br />\n香港最可憐的地方，不是被強迫做甚麼一國一制，而是逆潮流，行水尾，走在潮流的末端。<br />\n<br />\n就像全世界已經不再穿寬筒喇叭墊膊時，你卻奉為瑰寶。<br />\n<br />\n今天世界潮流是甚麼？就是齊聲向中共說「不」。注意，是「中共」，而不是「中國」，這個分別很大。美國告別過去<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n要求，居然來一個「新中國聯邦宣言」，要結束一黨。台灣選民高票罷免韓國瑜，除了因為他沒有做滿市長，也因為他親共路線被台灣人唾棄。台灣島討厭共產黨人數居高不下。<br />\n<br />\n（已節錄）<br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}